  - m_Id: 5438365886795776
    m_Localized: "Hi! \n<b>Thank you for trying Game Title!</b>\n\nTo help us improve
      the game, we collect <b>anonymous</b> gameplay data - things like level progress,
      scores, and which mechanics you use.\n\nWe only use this data to improve balance,
      stability, and overall game quality. <b>We do not collect personal details
      like your name or email.</b>\n\nYou can disable analytics anytime in Settings,
      and you can request deletion of your analytics data at any time.\nPlease read
      our Privacy Policy. for details."
